.SH NAME
std::experimental::pmr::monotonic_buffer_resource::monotonic_buffer_resource \- std::experimental::pmr::monotonic_buffer_resource::monotonic_buffer_resource

.SH Synopsis
   monotonic_buffer_resource();                                   \fB(1)\fP (library
